s></addrLine></address></div><div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><date>6. Juli 08</date>.</dateline><salute>Lieber Herr Bahr,</salute></opener><p><rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb2173">wir</rs> haben Ihr wunderschönes <rs type="work" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb30023">Feuilleton <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="KL107-1"/>über <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2309">Moppchen</rs><note type="commentary" xml:id="KL107-1h"><p><bibl><rs type="person" ref="#pmb10815">Hermann Bahr</rs>: <rs type="work" ref="#pmb30023">Moppchen</rs>. In: <rs type="org" ref="#pmb29351">Neue Freie Presse</rs>, Nr. 15757, <date>4. 7. 1908</date>. Morgenblatt, S. 1–5</bibl> (»Moppchen« war der Spitzname von <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2309">Katharina Hartleben</rs>).</p></note></rs> mit Ergriffenheit gelesen, schicken Ihnen die herzlichsten Grüsse und viel gute Wünsche für den Sommer.</p><closer><signed>Olga Schnitzler.</signed></closer></div><div type="writingSession" n="2"><p><handShift scribe="pmb2121"/>He<damage agent="hole"><supplied>rzl</supplied></damage>ichst dein <signed>Arthur</signed>.<pb/></p></div><div type="writingSession" n="3"><p><handShift scribe="pmb2173"/><anchor type="textConst" xml:id="TL107-1"/>Unser Balcon.<note type="textConst" xml:id="TL107-1h"><p>Auf dem Motiv mit einem Pfeil markiert.</p></note></p></div></body></text><back><listPerson><person xml:id="pmb2173"><persName><forename>Olga</forename><surname>Schnitzler</surname></persName><persName type="geburtsname_nachname">Gussmann</persName><persName type="pseudonym">Dina Marius</persName><persName type="legacy-name-merge">Schnitzler, Olga</persName><birth><date when="1882-01-17">17.01.1882</date><settlement ref="#pmb50"><placeName type="pref">Wien</placeName><location><geo>48,2066 16,37341</geo></location></settlement></birth><death><date when="1970-01-13">13.01.1970</date><settlement ref="#pmb885"><placeName type="pref">Lugano</placeName><location><geo>46,01008 8,96004</geo></location>